Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.iut.tapawaru.map.Map

  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    Map hosting the game. It's editable with the Terra' Spells. X-axis is xSize Y-axis is ySize [xSize][ySize]
